  "text": "In um trying to build an understanding from the start, you might say, starting with intelligent infinity and getting to our present condition of being. I am having some difficulty, but I think I should go back and investigate our Sun, since it is the sub-logos that creates all that we experience in this particular planetary system. Will you give me a description of the sun of our sun? I am pro this is a query which is not easily answered in your language for the Sun has a various aspect in a relation to intelligent infinity, a two intelligent energy, and a two each a density of each a planet, as you call these spheres. Moreover, these differences extend into the metaphysical or time space a part of your creation in a relationship to intelligent infinity. The Sun Body is equally with all parts of the infinite creation, part of that infinity in relation to the potentiated intelligent infinity, which makes use of intelligent energy. It is the offspring, shall we say, of the logos for a much larger number of a sub a logoi. The relationship is hierarchical in that the sub-logos uses the intelligent energy in ways set forth by the logos and uses its free will to cocreate the, shall we say, a full nuances of your densities as you experience them in relationship to the densities, the sun body may physically, as you would say, be seen to be a large body of gaseous elements undergoing the processes of effusion and radiating heat and a light. Thus by the sixth a density of the a sun may be visited and inhabited by those dwelling in time space and may even be partially created from a moment to moment by the processes of sixth density entities in their evolution.",
